  description="奇幻魔藥完整實測！RG電子蜂巢相鄰消除老虎機，RTP 98.28%業界天花板、最大x20000倍。6個相同符號相鄰即中獎，Wild累積倍數+魔藥缸加乘+15局Free Game全解析。"
  ogImage="https://game8la.com/images/fantasy-potion/cover.webp"
  currentPage="rankings"
>
<div class="container">
  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">首頁</a> &gt; <a href="/#games">熱門遊戲</a> &gt; 奇幻魔藥</div>
  <a href="/#games" class="back-link"><Icon name="arrow-left" /> 回遊戲列表</a>
  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:2rem;margin-bottom:2rem">
