      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;margin:1rem 0">
        <span class="score-big">9.7</span>
        <span class="stars" style="font-size:1.2rem"><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star" /><Icon name="star-half" /></span>
        <span style="color:var(--text-muted)">(9,874 次瀏覽)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <span class="label">遊戲供應商</span><span class="value">RG電子（RG Slot）</span>
        <span class="label">返還率 (RTP)</span><span class="value" style="color:var(--guava-green)">98.28%（業界天花板）</span>
        <span class="label">波動率</span><span class="value" style="color:var(--guava-pink)">高波動</span>
        <span class="label">最高倍率</span><span class="value" style="color:var(--gold-light)">x20,000</span>
        <span class="label">盤面結構</span><span class="value">蜂巢六角格（Honeycomb）</span>
        <span class="label">最低押注</span><span class="value">0.5 元起</span>
        <span class="label">中獎條件</span><span class="value">6 個以上相同符號上下左右相鄰</span>
        <span class="label">Wild</span><span class="value">常駐盤面中間，代替所有符號（Scatter 除外）</span>
        <span class="label">Scatter</span><span class="value">出現即觸發 15 局免費遊戲，重觸 +5 局</span>
